4. Php ton c bn

In[4]:
# Cc php ton s hc
print('7 + 2 =', 7 + 2)     # 9
print('7 - 2 =', 7 - 2)     # 5
print('7 * 2 =', 7 * 2)     # 14
print('7 / 2 =', 7 / 2)     # 3.5 (chia thc)
print('7 // 2 =', 7 // 2)   # 3 (chia nguyn)
print('7 % 2 =', 7 % 2)     # 1 (phn d)
print('7 ** 2 =', 7 ** 2)   # 49 (ly tha)

# Php ton bit
print('7 & 2 =', 7 & 2)     # 2 (AND)
print('7 | 2 =', 7 | 2)     # 7 (OR)
print('7 ^ 2 =', 7 ^ 2)     # 5 (XOR)
print('~7 =', ~7)           # -8 (NOT)

In[6]:
def tich(a, b=1):
    """Tnh tch hai s, b mc nh = 1"""
    return a * b

print(tich(10, 20))  # 200
print(tich(10))      # 10 (s dng b=1)
print(tich(a=5))     # 5
print(tich(b=6, a=5))  # 30 (keyword arguments)

PHN II: CU TRC D LIU

Kiu d liu tun t

  • Kiu d liu tun t: kiu d liu cha bn trong n cc d liu con nh hn v thng c x l bng cch ly ra tng phn-t-mt (bng vng for)
  • Cc kiu d liu cha bn trong n cc d liu nh hn thng c gi l cc container (b cha)
  • Khi nim tun t nhn vo vic x l tng phn t mt, nhng khng nht thit y l cch x l duy nht
  • C 3 kiu tun t thng dng l list, tuple v range
  • C nhiu kiu khc nh string, bytes, bytearray,hoc cc lp trnh vin c th t to kiu ring theo nhu cu .

# To dictionary
student = {
    'name': 'Nguyn Vn An',
    'age': 20,
    'grades': [8, 9, 7, 8.5],
    'info': {'class': 'CNTT01', 'year': 2024}
}

print(student.get('phone', 'N/A'))  # 'N/A' (khng c key 'phone')

# Dictionary methods
print(student.keys())       # dict_keys(['name', 'age', 'grades', 'info'])
print(student.values())     # dict_values([...])
print(student.items())      # dict_items([('name', 'Nguyn Vn An'), ...])

# Update dictionary
student.update({'phone': '0123456789', 'age': 21})
print(student['age'])       # 21

# Dictionary comprehension

print(squares_dict)  # {0: 0, 1: 1, 2: 4, 3: 9, 4: 16}

# Nested dictionary operations
grades_by_subject = {
    'Math': {'midterm': 8, 'final': 9},
    'Physics': {'midterm': 7, 'final': 8},
    'Chemistry': {'midterm': 9, 'final': 9}
}

for subject, scores in grades_by_subject.items():
    avg = (scores['midterm'] + scores['final']) / 2
    print(f"{subject}: {avg}")

print("Mng ngu nhin:")
print(random)

import numpy as np

x = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4]], dtype=np.float64)
y = np.array([[5, 6], [7, 8]], dtype=np.float64)

print("x + y (element-wise):") # Cng tng phn t
print(x + y)  # [[6, 8], [10, 12]]

print("\nx * y (element-wise):") # Nhn tng phn t
print(x * y)  # [[5, 12], [21, 32]]

print("\nnp.sqrt(x):") # Cn bc hai tng phn t
print(np.sqrt(x))  # [[1, 1.414], [1.732, 2]]

# Php nhn ma trn (dot product)
print("\nx.dot(y) (matrix multiplication):") 
print(x.dot(y))  # [[19, 22], [43, 50]]

# Vector operations
v = np.array([9, 10])
w = np.array([11, 12])
print(f"\nDot product v.w: {v.dot(w)}")  # 219 

# Ma trn chuyn v
print("\nChuyn v ca x:")
print(x.T) # [[1, 3], [2, 4]]

# Ma trn nghch o
print("\nNghch o ca x:")
print(np.linalg.inv(x)) # [[-2. , 1. ], [1.5, -0.5]]

6. Boolean indexing v fancy indexing

In[15]:
import numpy as np

# Boolean indexing
a = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]])
print("Mng a:")
print(a)

bool_idx = (a > 2) # To boolean mask
print("Boolean mask:")
print(bool_idx)

print("\nPhn t > 2:")
print(a[bool_idx])  # [3 4 5 6]

# Fancy indexing
a = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]])
indices = np.array([0, 1, 2]) # Chn hng 0, 1, 2
cols = np.array([0, 1, 0]) # Chn ct 0, 1, 0

print("\nFancy indexing a[indices, cols]:") # Chn a[0,0], a[1,1], a[2,0]
print(a[indices, cols])  # [1 4 5]

# Equivalent to:
print("Equivalent:")
print(np.array([a[0, 0], a[1, 1], a[2, 0]]))

Boolean mask:
[[False False]
 [ True  True]
 [ True  True]]

Phn t > 2:
[3 4 5 6]

Fancy indexing a[indices, cols]:
[1 4 5]
Equivalent:
[1 4 5]

7. Reshape v cc thao tc hnh dng

In[16]:
import numpy as np

# Reshape
x = np.array([[1, 2], [3, 4], [5, 6]])
print(f"Original shape: {x.shape}") # .shape kch thc mng

# Reshape thnh 2x3
y = x.reshape(2, 3) # To mng mi 2x3
print(f"Reshaped to 2x3:")
print(y)

# Reshape vi -1 (t ng tnh)
z = x.reshape(2, -1)  # T ng tnh chiu cn li
print(f"Shape with -1: {z.shape}")

# Flatten - chuyn thnh 1D

10. Indexing nng cao - iloc, loc

In[43]:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

# To DataFrame mu
df = pd.DataFrame({
    'A': range(5),
    'B': range(5, 10),
    'C': range(10, 15),
    'D': range(15, 20)
}, index=['row0', 'row1', 'row2', 'row3', 'row4'])

print("DataFrame gc:")
print(df)

# iloc - indexing by position (integer)
print(f"\niloc[0, 1] (hng 0, ct 1): {df.iloc[0, 1]}")
print(f"\niloc[1:3, 0:2] (hng 1-2, ct 0-1):")
print(df.iloc[1:3, 0:2])

# loc - indexing by label  
print(f"\nloc['row1', 'B']: {df.loc['row1', 'B']}")
print(f"\nloc['row1':'row3', 'A':'C']:")
print(df.loc['row1':'row3', 'A':'C'])

# Boolean indexing
print(f"\nBoolean indexing (A > 2):")
print(df[df['A'] > 2])

# Query method
print(f"\nQuery method:")
print(df.query('A > 2 & B < 9'))

row3  3  8  13  18
row4  4  9  14  19

iloc[0, 1] (hng 0, ct 1): 5

def one_day(my_nums, result, money):
    """Tnh ton mt ngy chi"""
    pay = len(my_nums) * money  # Tin t
    get = money * 70 if result in my_nums else 0  # Tin thng
    return get - pay

def many_days(my_nums, results, money):
    """Tnh ton nhiu ngy chi"""
    total = 0
    for result in results:
        total += one_day(my_nums, result, money)
    return total

# S dng d liu  to  trn
money = 1000
cuoi_data = cuoi_series.values

# Chin lc 1: Nui mt s
favorite_number = 76
profit_one = many_days([favorite_number], cuoi_data[:365], money)  # Nm u
profit_all = many_days([favorite_number], cuoi_data, money)        # Ton b

print(f"Chin lc nui s {favorite_number}:")
print(f"  Nm u: {profit_one:,} VN")
print(f"  Ton b: {profit_all:,} VN")

# Chin lc 2: Nui nhiu s
multiple_nums = [76, 92, 3, 10, 51, 45]
profit_multiple = many_days(multiple_nums, cuoi_data, money)
print(f"\nChin lc nui nhiu s {multiple_nums}:")
print(f"  Ton b: {profit_multiple:,} VN")

# Chin lc 3: Theo s ra nhiu nht
most_common = cuoi_series.value_counts().index[0]  # S xut hin nhiu nht
profit_common = many_days([most_common], cuoi_data, money)
print(f"\nChin lc theo s xut hin nhiu nht ({most_common}):")
print(f"  Ton b: {profit_common:,} VN")

import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn import linear_model, metrics

# To d liu mu (thay v c t file)
np.random.seed(42)
heights = np.random.normal(170, 10, 50)  # Chiu cao trung bnh 170cm
# Cn nng c tng quan vi chiu cao + noise
weights = 0.8 * heights - 100 + np.random.normal(0, 5, 50)

df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Cao': heights,
    'Nang': weights
})

print("D liu ngi (5 dng u):")
print(df.head())

# V scatter plot
plt.figure(figsize=(12, 8))
plt.subplot(2, 2, 1)
plt.scatter(df['Cao'], df['Nang'], c='blue', alpha=0.6)
plt.xlabel('Chiu cao (cm)')
plt.ylabel('Cn nng (kg)')
plt.title('D liu gc')
plt.grid(True)

# Chun b d liu cho model
X = df[['Cao']].values  # Features (phi l 2D array)
y = df['Nang'].values   # Target

# To v hun luyn model
model = linear_model.LinearRegression()
model.fit(X, y)

# nh gi model
y_pred = model.predict(X)
mse = metrics.mean_squared_error(y, y_pred)
r2 = metrics.r2_score(y, y_pred)

print(f"\nThng tin model:")
print(f"H s hi quy (slope): {model.coef_[0]:.4f}")
print(f"H s chn (intercept): {model.intercept_:.4f}")
print(f"Cng thc: Cn nng = {model.coef_[0]:.4f}  Chiu cao + {model.intercept_:.4f}")
print(f"Mean Squared Error: {mse:.2f}")
print(f"R Score: {r2:.4f}")

# V ng hi quy
plt.subplot(2, 2, 2)
plt.scatter(X, y, c='blue', alpha=0.6, label='D liu thc')
plt.plot(X, y_pred, color='red', linewidth=2, label='ng hi quy')
plt.xlabel('Chiu cao (cm)')
plt.ylabel('Cn nng (kg)')
plt.title('Linear Regression')
plt.legend()
plt.grid(True)

# D bo cho cc gi tr mi
test_heights = np.array([[160], [170], [180], [190]])
predictions = model.predict(test_heights)

print(f"\nD bo cn nng:")
for height, weight in zip(test_heights.flatten(), predictions):
    print(f"Chiu cao {height}cm  Cn nng d bo: {weight:.1f}kg")

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

2. Multiple Linear Regression - Thm yu t gii tnh

In[48]:
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from sklearn import linear_model, metrics

# To d liu mu vi gii tnh
np.random.seed(42)
n_samples = 100

heights = np.random.normal(170, 10, n_samples)
genders = np.random.choice(['Nam', 'N'], n_samples)

# To cn nng vi s khc bit gii tnh
weights = []
for height, gender in zip(heights, genders): # To cn nng da trn chiu cao v gii tnh
    base_weight = 0.8 * height - 100 # Cng thc c bn
    if gender == 'Nam':
        base_weight += 5  # Nam gii nng hn
    else:
        base_weight -= 3  # N gii nh hn
    
    # Thm noise
    weight = base_weight + np.random.normal(0, 3)
    weights.append(weight)

df = pd.DataFrame({
    'Cao': heights,
    'Gioitinh': genders,
    'Nang': weights
})

# Chuyn i gii tnh thnh s (Nam=1, N=0)
df['GT'] = df['Gioitinh'].apply(lambda x: 1 if x == 'Nam' else 0)

print("D liu vi gii tnh (5 dng u):")
print(df.head())

# Visualize d liu theo gii tnh
plt.figure(figsize=(15, 10))

plt.subplot(2, 3, 1)
nam_data = df[df['Gioitinh'] == 'Nam']
nu_data = df[df['Gioitinh'] == 'N']

plt.scatter(nam_data['Cao'], nam_data['Nang'], c='blue', alpha=0.6, label='Nam')
plt.scatter(nu_data['Cao'], nu_data['Nang'], c='red', alpha=0.6, label='N')
plt.xlabel('Chiu cao (cm)')
plt.ylabel('Cn nng (kg)')
plt.title('D liu theo gii tnh')
plt.legend()
plt.grid(True)

# Chun b d liu cho multiple regression
X = df[['Cao', 'GT']].values  # Features: chiu cao v gii tnh
y = df['Nang'].values         # Target: cn nng

# To v hun luyn model
model = linear_model.LinearRegression()
model.fit(X, y)

# nh gi model
y_pred = model.predict(X)
mse = metrics.mean_squared_error(y, y_pred)
r2 = metrics.r2_score(y, y_pred)

print(f"\nMultiple Linear Regression:")
print(f"H s hi quy: {model.coef_}")
print(f"  - Chiu cao: {model.coef_[0]:.4f}")
print(f"  - Gii tnh: {model.coef_[1]:.4f}")
print(f"H s chn: {model.intercept_:.4f}")
print(f"MSE: {mse:.2f}")
print(f"R Score: {r2:.4f}")

# Cng thc
print(f"\nCng thc:")
print(f"Cn nng = {model.coef_[0]:.4f}  Chiu cao + {model.coef_[1]:.4f}  Gii tnh + {model.intercept_:.4f}")
print(f"(Gii tnh: Nam=1, N=0)")

# So snh d bo cho nam v n
test_heights = [160, 170, 180]
print(f"\nD bo cn nng:")
print(f"{'Chiu cao':<12} {'Nam (kg)':<10} {'N (kg)':<10} {'Chnh lch':<12}")
print("-" * 50)

for height in test_heights:
    weight_male = model.predict([[height, 1]])[0]
    weight_female = model.predict([[height, 0]])[0]
    difference = weight_male - weight_female
    
    print(f"{height}cm{'':<7} {weight_male:<10.1f} {weight_female:<10.1f} {difference:<12.1f}")

# Visualize kt qu
plt.subplot(2, 3, 2)
plt.scatter(y, y_pred, alpha=0.6)
plt.plot([y.min(), y.max()], [y.min(), y.max()], 'r--', lw=2)
plt.xlabel('Cn nng thc t')
plt.ylabel('Cn nng d bo')
plt.title(f'D bo vs Thc t (R={r2:.3f})')
plt.grid(True)

# Residuals plot
plt.subplot(2, 3, 3)
residuals = y - y_pred
plt.scatter(y_pred, residuals, alpha=0.6)
plt.axhline(y=0, color='r', linestyle='--')
plt.xlabel('Cn nng d bo')
plt.ylabel('Residuals')
plt.title('Residuals Plot')
plt.grid(True)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
